","800 g water","1 vegetable stock cube (for 0.5 l)","1 pinch fine sea salt","250 g Arborio rice","1 pinch saffron threads","1 Tbsp water, hot"]},{"title":"Red Pesto","content":["150 g sun-dried tomatoes in oil, drained","20 g fresh basil leaves","60 g toasted pine nuts","1 garlic clove","1 pinch ground black pepper","40 - 50 g extra virgin olive oil, to taste"]},{"title":"Batter","content":["170 g plain flour","160 g water","1 medium egg"]},{"title":"Assembly","content":["frying oil (e.g. sunflower or vegetable)","200 g breadcrumbs (see tip)"]}],"id":"r247293","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-oem9LUr372M\/XZMvZupzxAI\/AAAAAAAAaRY\/QqQpKI6CfZgLcWAv7vOgrixsF2ISg2eXQCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_fltVD2vgROUe0oDU.png","title":"Arancini","publishedAt":"2018-05-28T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"9.1 g","fat":"21.9 g","uom":"per 1 piece","carbohydrates":"34.5 g","calories":"1569 kJ \/ 376 kcal"},"usefulItems":"slotted spoon, paper towels, deep saucepan or deep fat fryer, jug, refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["To make your own breadcrumbs, place <b>200 g<b> bread in mixing bowl and grate <strong><b>10 sec\/speed 10<b><\/strong>.","Any leftover pesto can be stored in an airtight jar in the fridge for up to <b>5 days<b>. Enjoy with pasta, spread a layer on a salmon fillet or use to stuff a chicken breast.","To make this recipe suitable for vegetarians, substitute the Parmesan cheese for a vegetarian hard cheese.","Part of traditional southern Italian cuisine for centuries, arancini are large rice balls that are stuffed with a savoury filling then coated in breadcrumbs and deep fried. Fillings vary from region to region but one of the most popular is a rich meat ragù with peas. Arancini that are formed with mozzarella in the centre are called <i>arancini di riso al telefono<\/i> due to the mozzarella forming a long string like a telephone line when broken apart.","Add <b>1 cm<b> cubes of mozzarella in the middle of the arancini for extra flavour."],"basicInfo":["medium","45m","2h 10m","14 pieces"]}